{"tid":750470,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大劉鬧殯儀之星博宣傳","createTime":"2018-07-21T02:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T13:54:23.000Z","uid":82917,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8a82b255a3953532fa6368a42dd70bb6ca18f327","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:18:37.000Z","msg":"《殯儀之星，即係人地有錢、有價值就死都要黐埋去！咪要去抬起其他人，去同其他女人上床囉》大劉昨日出席佳士得拍賣預展時，再度爆發創作力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉鑾雄昨日到金鐘萬豪酒店，出席佳士得拍賣預展。談到陳百祥前日讚他說話有point時，大劉笑說：「重有好多例子，好似『黐枱王』同『殯儀之星』咁。何謂『黐枱王』？就係早排有個超級富豪食飯，有人黐埋枱度博影相。何謂『殯儀之星』呢？譬如蓋茨（BillGates）有親戚死咗，有人就飛去西雅圖，天未光就入殯儀館同BillGates影相囉，即係人哋有錢，有價值就死都要黐埋去。」<br />\n<br />\n白事不應變宣傳 <br />\n大劉又表示不會出席羅文喪禮，他說：「唔去，我驚俾人話我擅闖私人地方，容乜易俾人打一身，報警話我騷擾。某商人出晒錢定出部份錢，我都想八吓。不過，好似羅文咁重份量嘅藝人，如果係我員工，佢有病，我一定由佢病嗰日開始出錢醫佢，糧照出。不過我啲員工唔係藝人，我幫完就算，係心意，唔係將幫助當宣傳，攞嚟日日見報。如果真係一個朋友，唔應該將紅事、白事攞嚟宣傳。 <br />\n「做我員工，打工仔黎架咋！邊個係我老婆女朋友呀？唔使好似孖Q、四重彩、六合彩、三連環咁，陪我嘅商界朋友瞓覺，唔使喺我指令下去某酒店開房，我冇咁嘅需要同客路，亦做唔出，都唔會將唔聽話員工放逐。」<br />\n<br />\n黐枱王不斷挑釁 <br />\n近日創作力驚人的大劉，昨笑言要多謝「殯儀之星」及「黐枱王」不斷挑釁，提供創作和爆料的能量和動力給他。大劉說：「我真係恭喜佢！耐唔耐就有雜誌鐵證乜、力證物，啲又殘又舊嘅報紙又話我前女友點樣點樣，即係好似香港變咗巴勒斯坦，佢用『港式人肉炸彈』炸我，我就爆啲堅料回應。」"},{"pid":"f99be986ca92c2363eae03663f84587a1841c158","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:18:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20021027/2910486\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20021027%2F2910486&d=%2Bo3dCIM5i4F2u9Sbvt8AmwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5c0c3e30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20021027%2F2910486&h=51ba1afa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20021027/2910486</a>"},{"pid":"bcdbcd7ed1ed75b6ae1d43f4c770fb4a321d8488","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:25:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大劉金口起朵逐個睇！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">殯儀之星 </span><br />\n即係有價值就死都要黐埋去。而「<span style=\"color: red;\">黐枱王</span>」就係早排有個超級富豪食飯，有人黐埋枱度博影相。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">二五仔之王 </span><br />\n大家都知係邊個，即係早幾日向全港六百萬市民報流料嗰個，重有一個「<span style=\"color: red;\">二五仔之后</span>」，凡對上流社會有啲認識嘅人，都會對佢有印象。 <br />\n<br />\n我遲啲喺中環掃街，咪做埋香港揸弗人？ <br />\n<br />\n唔通我怕你發霉大佬係黑社會，有牙老鼠呀？ <br />\n<br />\n呢個放料人係「<span style=\"color: red;\">專業小雞</span>」，因為經濟唔好，只要喺佢平時收開嘅專業服務費之外再加多十萬八萬，佢就肯同人多次上床。咁多聯絡架？唔洗講野啦我地！<br />\n<br />\n係「<span style=\"color: red;\">活死人</span>」報料畀「<span style=\"color: red;\">六月飛霜</span>」。不過&times;&times;都係俾人利用，𠵱家佢有得見吓報都可以生活得好開心。 <br />\n<br />\n某人不嬲都唔怕面懵，當香港六百萬市民係白癡，佢做得出㗎！ <br />\n<br />\n全港都知道某商人最叻就係「<span style=\"color: red;\">練縮骨神功</span>」，上身飛撲，下盤就畀石屎lock住，上半身就好姿勢，下半身就好實際。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">縮骨神功係「殯儀之星」性格，佢唔係出唔起，佢專門搵人笨。 </span><br />\n<br />\n如果我放料，絕子絕孫！"},{"pid":"1f23e95f89edcb3bbcc6f1be50254a9216d19c16","tid":750470,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"花名list有冇樓主份？"},{"pid":"dd188d96ae374b4a968f1656028d0295f55479ce","tid":750470,"uid":71166,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"成日幫人起花名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b440fd95a058dff6b496224351d919199035a8","tid":750470,"uid":39706,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:36:48.000Z","msg":"其實即係指邊個?  全部都唔明...  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2409bf041b9c860f4e1d290db255429ca0c6a3","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1f23e95f89edcb3bbcc6f1be50254a9216d19c16","tid":750470,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"花名list有冇樓主份？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:36:53.000Z","msg":"洪欣就有！大劉撚敢幫我改花名咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dc688d9da494724530f10efb964ee3591fff93","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd188d96ae374b4a968f1656028d0295f55479ce","tid":750470,"uid":71166,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"成日幫人起花名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:37:25.000Z","msg":"好撚頂癮喎弘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec2619d8b399286046000632b7c62942e2d92ac","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"92b440fd95a058dff6b496224351d919199035a8","tid":750470,"uid":39706,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:36:48.000Z","msg":"其實即係指邊個?  全部都唔明...  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:37:41.000Z","msg":"Google啦屌，有無咁懶"},{"pid":"8000c6028711f1ff816a82883f371e9a370f14c3","tid":750470,"uid":56716,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:42:15.000Z","msg":"至於劉鑾雄昨日在報章上直指有人借羅文的喪禮博宣傳，更稱對方為「殯儀之星」，昨午Twins出席壽司店活動時，鍾欣桐（阿嬌）說：「其實我冇乜點睇篇報道，其實咁慘仲要話乜之星，我覺得佢先係『殯儀之星』！」而在旁的蔡卓妍聽到阿嬌的一番話亦顯得有點愕然，只不停重複地說：「我唔知呀！」事後，阿嬌自知失言闖了禍，表示不想有不必要誤會。<br />\n<br />\n阿嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e7e8b078953bb04d66c7f3e60ee86fba845c06","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"8000c6028711f1ff816a82883f371e9a370f14c3","tid":750470,"uid":56716,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:42:15.000Z","msg":"至於劉鑾雄昨日在報章上直指有人借羅文的喪禮博宣傳，更稱對方為「殯儀之星」，昨午Twins出席壽司店活動時，鍾欣桐（阿嬌）說：「其實我冇乜點睇篇報道，其實咁慘仲要話乜之星，我覺得佢先係『殯儀之星』！」而在旁的蔡卓妍聽到阿嬌的一番話亦顯得有點愕然，只不停重複地說：「我唔知呀！」事後，阿嬌自知失言闖了禍，表示不想有不必要誤會。<br />\n<br />\n阿嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:43:03.000Z","msg":"呀SA：咁蠢既。。西。。西女人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b4d361cffd67e9ebdbd28a981b7b29a381479b","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"不過改人花名者亦被人改其花名，傳媒亦替大劉改了兩個花名：一個是「劉懸紅」，意思是大劉喜歡懸紅搜集他人的證據；另一個是「大樓」，因為他出手闊綽，喜歡送樓給朋友，除了紅顏知己外，連司機、船長等都受惠。 <br />\n大劉過往一直低調，直至前年初，其前妻寶詠琴在本報刊出自傳系列大爆家事，大劉認為她影響到一對子女，故接受亞視《香港睇真D》訪問，一句「<span style=\"color: red;\">阿琴，你心地唔好咁毒啦！</span>」，揭開了大劉在娛樂版見報的序幕，及後每逢有大劉出場，定必轟動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據知， 有晚寶詠琴與劉鑾雄在家晚飯， 電話響起， 寶小姐接聽， 對方不停講粗口， 「 屌你老母， 屌你老母&hellip; &hellip; 」 共說了九句。"},{"pid":"fab7e180f24aa67a163957041a1f46f495bb7b90","tid":750470,"uid":182286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0567e0d3acc89d969f1b91fba60b0ecc717756e5","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"前年年中，劉鑾雄和富豪團遊日本，因為有人報料給傳媒令行蹤曝光，李<span style=\"color: red;\">洪芷晴</span>是最大的嫌疑人物，她卻公然指大劉才是報料者，引發二人罵戰。大劉更懸紅一百萬揭李洪芷晴的「底牌」，最後李洪芷晴匿藏新加坡。 <br />\n而最震驚全城的，是前年年底羅兆輝燒炭自殺不遂，有傳是大劉向羅追債，大劉否認之餘，並聲討「老千商人」，懸紅三千萬美金（約兩億三千萬港元）揪出對方的罪證，創下香港開埠以來最高懸紅紀錄，引起警方高度關注。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">姓洪個啲都係閪女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"da4db90dfe007dee8d4b116881632b8843faf637","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fab7e180f24aa67a163957041a1f46f495bb7b90","tid":750470,"uid":182286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e7e8b078953bb04d66c7f3e60ee86fba845c06","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"8000c6028711f1ff816a82883f371e9a370f14c3","tid":750470,"uid":56716,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:42:15.000Z","msg":"至於劉鑾雄昨日在報章上直指有人借羅文的喪禮博宣傳，更稱對方為「殯儀之星」，昨午Twins出席壽司店活動時，鍾欣桐（阿嬌）說：「其實我冇乜點睇篇報道，其實咁慘仲要話乜之星，我覺得佢先係『殯儀之星』！」而在旁的蔡卓妍聽到阿嬌的一番話亦顯得有點愕然，只不停重複地說：「我唔知呀！」事後，阿嬌自知失言闖了禍，表示不想有不必要誤會。<br />\n<br />\n阿嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:43:03.000Z","msg":"呀SA：咁蠢既。。西。。西女人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:47:06.000Z","msg":"但係而家已經長大喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd4fe280aefedbf6d493647bc377c40b5b477d6","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"楊受成劉鑾雄被曝誘女星任港秀脫衣<br />\r\n2008-11-06<br />\r\n<br />\r\n港商羅兆輝曾自曝和香港性感女星任港秀的一段祕聞，他還稱自己和大哥(劉鑾雄)、受哥(楊受成)三個人曾湊齊一千萬元引誘任港秀脫衣。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n港商羅兆輝曾爆料自己和香港性感女星任港秀的一段祕聞。据稱，當時身在英國倫敦的羅兆輝，本打算偕任港秀飛往巴黎繼續歐洲之旅，但二人把臂同游的消息一經泄露后，任港秀即不辭而別，羅兆輝更自曝猛料，他說:&ldquo;我給一千萬叫她馬上脫衣，她沒有答應。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n楊受成 <br />\n就《東周刊》刊登女藝人裸照的風波，雜誌老闆楊受成由北韓回港後，向公眾道歉，同時表示要將《東周刊》停刊，他說：「我非常痛心，好似親手將個親生仔殺死咁，非常心痛！」<br />\n<br />\n張栢芝 <br />\n張栢芝在中環政府總部集會時，為譴責《東周刊》刊登女星被強迫拍下的裸照一事，一時意難平，和女Fans傾談時，愈說愈激動，一度失控大罵楊受成說：「打擊楊受成個仆街！」此語一出，現場記者即鴉雀無聲，為栢芝當眾爆粗驚訝不已，而栢芝亦自知說話失控，即時縮回車內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前啲新聞真係令人忍俊不禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80777db6a1d6b2fa37f02e6f14e50bd2c84b80ca","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"8000c6028711f1ff816a82883f371e9a370f14c3","tid":750470,"uid":56716,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:42:15.000Z","msg":"至於劉鑾雄昨日在報章上直指有人借羅文的喪禮博宣傳，更稱對方為「殯儀之星」，昨午Twins出席壽司店活動時，鍾欣桐（阿嬌）說：「其實我冇乜點睇篇報道，其實咁慘仲要話乜之星，我覺得佢先係『殯儀之星』！」而在旁的蔡卓妍聽到阿嬌的一番話亦顯得有點愕然，只不停重複地說：「我唔知呀！」事後，阿嬌自知失言闖了禍，表示不想有不必要誤會。<br />\n<br />\n阿嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:54:11.000Z","msg":"「各為其主應該咁做」 <br />\n大劉獲悉阿嬌暗指他是「殯儀之星」，他昨日在電話中說：「出得人哋人工，各為其主，應該咁做，否則返去俾人炒魷魚。做得『殯儀之星』要成日出現殯儀館，又要做得出位先有資格競選。我十幾廿年去過殯儀館一、兩次，如果咁都有資格，有啲人咪升級做『殯儀之星』星中星嘅星星星？」<br />\n<br />\n一路搵一路笑，痴撚線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6d775aa700ae5ce59fef7e6e3b6925692f0a26","tid":750470,"uid":21716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4bd4fe280aefedbf6d493647bc377c40b5b477d6","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"楊受成劉鑾雄被曝誘女星任港秀脫衣<br />\r\n2008-11-06<br />\r\n<br />\r\n港商羅兆輝曾自曝和香港性感女星任港秀的一段祕聞，他還稱自己和大哥(劉鑾雄)、受哥(楊受成)三個人曾湊齊一千萬元引誘任港秀脫衣。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n港商羅兆輝曾爆料自己和香港性感女星任港秀的一段祕聞。据稱，當時身在英國倫敦的羅兆輝，本打算偕任港秀飛往巴黎繼續歐洲之旅，但二人把臂同游的消息一經泄露后，任港秀即不辭而別，羅兆輝更自曝猛料，他說:&ldquo;我給一千萬叫她馬上脫衣，她沒有答應。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n楊受成 <br />\n就《東周刊》刊登女藝人裸照的風波，雜誌老闆楊受成由北韓回港後，向公眾道歉，同時表示要將《東周刊》停刊，他說：「我非常痛心，好似親手將個親生仔殺死咁，非常心痛！」<br />\n<br />\n張栢芝 <br />\n張栢芝在中環政府總部集會時，為譴責《東周刊》刊登女星被強迫拍下的裸照一事，一時意難平，和女Fans傾談時，愈說愈激動，一度失控大罵楊受成說：「打擊楊受成個仆街！」此語一出，現場記者即鴉雀無聲，為栢芝當眾爆粗驚訝不已，而栢芝亦自知說話失控，即時縮回車內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前啲新聞真係令人忍俊不禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/105719_2c159ded0f91ad523f33e12171b69c6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F105719_2c159ded0f91ad523f33e12171b69c6a.png&h=c4fc257f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5a8ad3edef1e3c8ed03e0d9f22e935791668cd1","tid":750470,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464a89f3ffcc3b22dd7e2b4da0db8dd0ad4358fd","tid":750470,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da4db90dfe007dee8d4b116881632b8843faf637","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fab7e180f24aa67a163957041a1f46f495bb7b90","tid":750470,"uid":182286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e7e8b078953bb04d66c7f3e60ee86fba845c06","tid":750470,"uid":82917,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:43:03.000Z","msg":"呀SA：咁蠢既。。西。。西女人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:47:06.000Z","msg":"但係而家已經長大喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki